text: Dioon angustifolium is a species of cycad that is endemic to Tamaulipas and Nuevo León, Mexico. ==Distribution== Plants occur in two main areas: *the Sierra Madre Oriental and the Sierra de San Carlos, Sierra Tamaulipas *low hills in the vicinity of Soto la Marina, Tamaulipas ==References== ==External links== * * angustifolium Category:Flora of Mexico
title: Dioon angustifolium
